# Audio Speech API

## Endpoint
POST {{.BaseURL}}/v1/audio/speech

## Description
Generates audio from input text.

## Authentication
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY

## Example Request
```bash
curl {{.BaseURL}}/v1/audio/speech \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY" \
  -d '{
    "model": "tts-1",
    "input": "Hello world",
    "voice": "alloy"
  }'
```

## Parameters
- **model** (required): TTS model (tts-1, tts-1-hd)
- **input** (required): Text to generate audio for
- **voice** (required): Voice option (alloy, echo, fable, onyx, nova, shimmer)
